        Applicant: ${formData.scholar.fullName}
        PhD Subject: ${formData.program.phdSubject}
        Bond: ${formData.program.serviceYears} years

        Provide constructive feedback and a score out of 100.
        Return ONLY valid JSON: {"feedback": "string", "score": number}`,
        config: { responseMimeType: 'application/json' }
